'''''One Night in Vegas''''' ni filime yikinamico yo muri [[Nigeriya]] 2013 iyobowe na John Uche. Irimo Jimmy Jean-Louis,    John Dumelo, Yvonne Nelson,   Sarodj Bertin, Van Vicker, Michael Blackson na Koby Maxwell .   Filime yibanze ku Bashakanye bo muri [[Gana]] bagerageza kunoza umubano wabo bafata urugendo i Las Vegas. Iyi filime yakozwe n'itsinda rimwe ryerekanye <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paparazzi_Eye_in_the_Dark" rel="mw:ExtLink" title="Paparazzi Eye in the Dark" class="mw-redirect cx-link" data-linkid="102">Paparazzi Eye in the Dark</a> mu 2011.  Biteganijwe ku ngengo y’imari ntoya kandi ifatwa amashusho mu gihe cyiminsi 19, iyi filime yamenyekanye ku isoko rya Nollywood USA  kubera ko iyi filime yiteguye kuzamura umurongo wa filime nyafurika  ikoresheje inzira y’iburengerazuba. ku bwiza bw'umusaruro n'ibipimo.  By'umwihariko gukoresha uburambe bw'umukinnyi w'amafirime w'umunyamerika (Tim " Black Magic Tim " Wilson)  kugirango akore Cinematografi na Muhinduzi.  filimi yarekuwe kumugaragaro muri [[Gana|Ghana]] yari ubwa mbere hasohotse turnout mu mateka ya Silverbird Theatre mu Accra Mall . 

Film yerekanywe ku muryango w'Abibumbye i New York City,  Ku Library of Congress mu Washington DC,  Mu Pan Film Festival [[Afurika]],  Dublin muri Irlande,  Haiti,  [[Nigeria]] ku Nyakanga 18, 2014,   Maryland, Virginia, California, Ubwongereza, Afurika y'Epfo, na Siyera Lewone.

